          How long does it take to sell a home in Camp Hill?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Camp Hill homes typically sell within 28 to 45 days. The suburb draws a competitive buyer pool given its proximity to the CBD, the Whites Hill Reserve and its reputation as one of the inner east's most liveable addresses.</p>
